'''''Iron Lord''''' is an [[Adventure game|adventure video game]] developed by Orou Mama and Ivan Jacot for the [[Atari ST]] and published by [[Ubi Soft]] in 1989. It was ported to the [[Amiga]], [[Acorn Archimedes]], [[Amstrad CPC]], [[Commodore 64]], [[ZX Spectrum]], and [[MS-DOS]].

==Reception==
{{Video game reviews
